                        <article class="welcome col-md-9 col-sm-8"><h2 style="text-align: center"><a href="http://beardsleyschool.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/28/2020/04/April-EOM-Breakfast-and-Lunch.pdf"><span style="color: #008000"><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline">GRAB &amp; GO  MENU FOR APRIL</span></strong></span></a></h2>
<p> </p>
<p style="text-align: center"><strong>School Meal Service during Covid-19 (Coronavirus) School Closures</strong></p>
<p>Beginning Monday, April 6<sup>th</sup>, Beardsley is making a change to its drive-thru meal service.  <u>All drive-thru Grab &amp; Go meals will be served at the Junior High School only!</u>  The entrance to this drive thru is located at the bus garage.  Please look for the flag-person near the entrance.  This change is being made in order to be more efficient with Beardsley staff and provide a much needed break for volunteers serving meals.  Walk up meals will continue to be served at all campuses and crossing guards will remain working during serving times.</p>
<h3 style="text-align: center">
<strong>No cost meals to-go </strong><strong>  10:30 to 12:00<u></u></strong>
</h3>
<h3 style="text-align: center">
<strong> </strong><strong>Starting April 20<sup>th   </sup>thru  May 22<sup>nd</sup>   – Serving meals Monday thru Thursday only</strong>
</h3>
<p> </p>
<h3 style="text-align: center">
<strong> </strong><strong><u>Walkers from home only 10:30 – 12:00  </u></strong>
</h3>
<h3 style="text-align: center">
<strong>North Beardsley Elementary – 900 Sanford Dr.</strong><br><strong>San Lauren Elementary – 5210 Victor St.</strong>
</h3>
<h3></h3>
<p> </p>
<h3 style="text-align: center"><strong><u>Drive-thru meals only &amp; walkers from home 10:30 – 12:00  </u></strong></h3>
<h3 style="text-align: center"><strong>Beardsley Junior High – 1001 Roberts Ln.</strong></h3>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Beardsley School District, Nutrition Services Department</strong> will provide an opportunity for families with children 2 years of age to 18 year old (ID may be required to verify under 18 years of age) to drive through or walk up to pick up meals for the children in their family, <strong>at no cost</strong>, at a number of school sites listed above.</p>
<p>Children must be present in order for meals to be provided. Meals will be served between 10:30 am and 12:00 pm, during the dates above. We will be serving a lunch for that day and a breakfast for the next day at each participating school. At <strong>Beardsley Junior High</strong> there will be a drive thru for families to take meals to go. Please stay in your car and meals will be passed through to you based on the number of children in the car with you. If you are walking, please go to the pick-up table to receive meals.</p>
<p> </p>
<p style="text-align: center"><strong>Breakfast and Lunch meals will be provided for free to children 2 years old to 18 years old.<br>
Children need to be present to receive meals.<br></strong><strong>Meal service is “Grab N Go” and may not be consumed on premises.</strong></p>
<p> </p>
